<p>The <em>OSCYS</em> database includes over a thousand documents covering 255 different case files. Importantly though, only 38% of the case files in the <em>OSCYS</em> database include more than three documents, while only a few quite exceptional case files include more than ten documents. This means that the majority of the case files consist primarily of only a few standard documentary types. In fact, just two types of document&#8212; petitions for freedom and summonses&#8212;dominate the database, making up 68% of its total collection.</p>

